text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "We see it in the coarsening of our political debate, dominated by abuse, threats and those who shout the loudest. We see it in the toxic discourse around immigration, where immigrants are blamed for all our problems. We see it in the rising tide of hate crime."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "For too long we have been defensive about our progressive politics - that kind hearted, progressive Britain which is generous in spirit, and should be open to new ideas and people of different backgrounds, is under threat like never before."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "As the new @OpiniumResearch polling which James and his team will set out shortly illustrates, progressive ideas and values are alive and well, and command popular support in our country."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: RT @UKProgressive: @ChukaUmunna  ‚ÄúCentrists stand accused of trying to maintain the status quo, when the opposite is true. Progressive idea‚Ä¶
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: RT @UKProgressive: @ChukaUmunna ‚ÄúPeople are tired and fed up about Brexit- but we must not dance to the populists tune. The only way to bre‚Ä¶
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "Because we are patriots, we are internationalist too. We will protect the sovereignty of the nation state which is the UK but we cannot build a good society at home in isolation from the global forces which are buffeting our people around."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "The populist left views much our mainstream media as a huge inconvenience, we view a free press as vital in our democracy. On the populist Right, the rule of law and an independent judiciary are denounced as ‚Äúenemies of the people", we see them as integral to our democracy."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "But there is more to life than work. Family life, in all its forms, and the importance of the place where people live are the building blocks of the communitarian ideals to which all progressives subscribe."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "Work not only provides us with the means to prosper economically but it has a value in and of itself that gives purpose, identity and mission in life. Our mission in policy terms should therefore be to ensure work pays and provides a level of security in a fast-changing world."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "Reciprocity is vital. So, as an individual if you put in the graft and play by the rules, the economy will reward you, and in return for the support we enjoy from society through the state, we all have individual responsibilities."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "Collectively we should ensure everyone is provided with the tools to reach their full potential to live a life they have reason to value, and where those who cannot provide for themselves are properly supported. So we stick together - we look out for our fellow citizens."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch @TheIndGroup "I set out six key values underpin in the @UKProgressive pamphlet: a United Kingdom; reciprocity; work; family and community; democracy; and patriotic internationalism."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "It led us to the inescapable conclusion that our politics needs to be reconfigured to better reflect modern Britain and that was time for the different progressive political traditions to come together under one roof ‚Äì a new progressive party. Change UK." @TheIndGroup
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: RT @jonwillchambers: Great to be at the launch of @ChukaUmunna‚Äôs ‚ÄòWhat are progressives for?‚Äô pamphlet at @UKProgressive with new research‚Ä¶
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "The main parties have ceased to be the broad churches the main parties is a two party electoral system need to be in order for our political system to function properly. It is why we left them. We were driven out because they had turned their backs on progressive values."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "Historically there has been a vibrant progressive political tradition in our country. It is rooted in the social democratic centre-Left, the liberal, and One Nation Conservative centre-Right which has successfully worked together in times past to see our country through crises."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "On the other side there is progressive Britain, which believes we tackle these problems by being open to new ideas and people, inclusive, forward looking and determined to embrace the future for the sake of our children."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "This is at the heart of the xenophobic, backward looking nationalism of Nigel Farage, the Brexit Party, UKIP, and I'm sorry to say has been adopted wholesale by the governing party the Conservatives."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "In the face of this change and disruption there is a real risk that instead of coming together as we have done in the past and rebuilding, the UK responds to the challenges of the globalisation not by asking ‚Äòhow can we solve these problems?‚Äô but by asking ‚Äòwho can we blame?"
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: RT @UKProgressive: @ChukaUmunna ‚ÄúThese European elections are about so much more than Leave and Remain. It‚Äôs about who we are as a nation,‚Ä¶
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "The 2016 Brexit vote was a symptom, not the cause of how people felt about all of this. The irony is that so consuming has Brexit been, that so many of our country‚Äôs problems have simply not received the attention they deserve."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "The long-term trend towards each citizen enjoying a more equal share of the national wealth has gone into reverse. We have not invested sufficiently in or have appropriate skills and training systems to help people adapt to what is happening."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "Globalisation has raised the standard of living of countless millions of poor people around the world. But in advanced economies like Britain it has brought wealth to too few and insecurity to millions on low and middle incomes."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "We are diverse but we are divided. The political and cultural divides, between the urban and the rural, our cities and our towns, the young and the old, between those with varying levels of educational qualifications, different ethnicities and classes is there for all to see."
users.description: Managing Director & Head of EMEA ESG @JPMorgan | Views my own
users.name: ChukaUmunna

text: @UKProgressive @OpiniumResearch "The vision presented to the world was a country at ease with itself, not only proud of our history but proud of what we have become ‚Äì open, humorous, decent, confident and modern. That is the Britain I love."
